Package: rivendell-cloud-installer
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: xrdp, icecast2, jackd2, qjackctl, liquidsoap, vlc, vlc-plugin-jack, mariadb-server
Description: Meta-installer for Rivendell 4.3.0 with custom stack and configs
 This package orchestrates the installation and configuration of Rivendell 4.3.0
 and related broadcasting tools, applying opinionated defaults and optional
 security hardening. It uses debconf to prompt for install type, hostname,
 timezone, and security choices. For fully offline installs, use the makeself
 bundle included in this repository.
